	<text>
		<body>
			<note xml:id="q-dc65e5fb-0a7d-e311-a968-000bdb5cc6d5" type="heading1" n="1"
				>Reflection</note>
			<u xml:id="q-dd65e5fb-0a7d-e311-a968-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="2">While looking out of my
				bedroom window I <sic>spoted</sic><corr>spotted</corr> a young girl walking her dog across the common. She was wearing
				a pair leged trousers it brought to mind the times when I used to wear the kind of
				clothes.</u>
			<u xml:id="q-de65e5fb-0a7d-e311-a968-000bdb5cc6d5" who="R" n="3">I remember well it was
				just about time when I got a job as an office in a local insurance company within
				four years I was secretary to the managing Director. At this time I was looking for
				job along the line of manager.</u>
		</body>
